    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and an inspected subframe, maintaining the legendary 50/50 weight distribution and sharp turn-in characteristic of the platform. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
